{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>逆波兰表达式是一种把运算符前置的算术表达式，例如普通的表达式2 + 3的逆波兰表示法为+ 2 3。逆波兰表达式的优点是运算符之间不必有优先级关系，也不必用括号改变运算次序，例如(2 + 3) \\* 4的逆波兰表示法为\\* + 2 3 4。本题求解逆波兰表达式的值，其中运算符包括+ - \\* /四个。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"逆波兰表达式 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出为一行，表达式的值。<p><p>可直接用printf(\"%f\\\\n\", v)输出表达式的值v。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入为一行，其中运算符和运算数之间都用空格分隔，运算数是浮点数。<p>","examples":"<input>\\* + 11.0 12.0 + 24.0 35.0\n</input><output>1357.000000\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1198","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}